{"tid":1839304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有事就醫護人員 無事就黃醫黃醫","createTime":"2020-01-24T10:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T12:12:17.000Z","uid":27814,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc607a767bdcd940de4200f296571a0a7adc362","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護人員的「無私精神」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有事就警察 無事就黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"fbd17b8c68ec34d1c514a0defaf29b8e74bec577","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cc607a767bdcd940de4200f296571a0a7adc362","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護人員的「無私精神」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有事就警察 無事就黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"文：龔靜儀<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月23日晚上，香港醫管局員工陣線聯同其他醫療組織發表聲明，就特區政府的武漢肺炎防疫工作作出回應。醫管局員工陣線的代表大肆批評特區政府沒有做好邊境的把關工作，導致了疫情傳入了香港，並揚言要求政府落實禁止內地旅客入境香港，並要在年初四前全面落實邊境防疫措施; 否則，組織將發起工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n回看在2003年，香港爆發沙士，共奪去了299條性命，當中有8位是醫護人員，包括被譽為「香港女兒」的屯門醫院胸肺科主任醫生謝婉雯。 1986年，謝婉雯醫生以會考8優成績，循暫取生途徑，入讀了中文大學醫學院。當年，她在入學手冊中寫下了: 「 加入醫生的行列，為社會和人民服務，更發揮自己所長。」至2003年沙士爆發，謝婉雯醫生更是主動請纓到深切治療部照顧病人。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謝婉雯醫生無私的精神</span></strong>，多年以來都備受香港各界人士所推崇！<br />\n<br />\n在享有民主和高度自治的香港社會，任何個人或團體提出他們對政府施政及推行措施的意見，予特區政府參考，當然是無任歡迎。但如果像今次新型冠狀病毒疫情，那些醫護界組織一樣，在說出自己的要求時，也一拼提出一個日子，作為死線，以一些<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">漠視甚至損害廣大香港市民利益的行動作為要脅，強行要特區政府接納他們的要求！為</span></strong>何醫護要左閃右避以罷工作要脅，棄病人如草芥? 要是香港所有團體、工會、機構也像他們一樣，用威脅的方式要求特區政府對他們事事順從，則最後的結果，還不是會拖垮整個香港社會？"},{"pid":"94ced2da740eb5c8032564dc1216ecac56445a54","tid":1839304,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"黑護黑媒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802ff2333a04bc7beaaa189d98b5cbafa15cb60e","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"藍屍：黃醫 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出事就：醫護人員救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7080e2cfee745bfd88c117326de51d8cfac7fc67","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ced2da740eb5c8032564dc1216ecac56445a54","tid":1839304,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"黑護黑媒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"係喎 黑記"},{"pid":"7db69bb5426a709f225bcd28db3c15f1f8cc81af","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"802ff2333a04bc7beaaa189d98b5cbafa15cb60e","tid":1839304,"uid":27814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"藍屍：黃醫 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出事就：醫護人員救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"藍屍：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑護 </span></span>不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出事就：醫護人員救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p